{"comments":"Roughness - surface roughness for PBR materials.\n\nRange: 0.0 to 1.0 (clamps)\n- **0.0**: Perfectly smooth (mirror-like reflections)\n- **0.3**: Glossy (polished metal, wet surfaces)\n- **0.7**: Rough (concrete, fabric)\n- **1.0**: Completely diffuse (matte, no specular)\n\nControls microfacet distribution in PBR shading models (GGX, Beckmann).\nUsed in Unreal, Unity, Cinema4D, Blender, Arnold, etc.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[71,1]},"title":"eqRoughness"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[72,1]},"title":"ordRoughness"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[74,1]},"title":"showRoughness"}],"comments":"Surface roughness for PBR (0.0 to 1.0)\n\nControls how rough a surface appears. Smooth surfaces have sharp reflections,\nrough surfaces have diffuse, blurred reflections.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[69,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[69,1]},"title":"Roughness"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a roughness value, clamping to 0.0-1.0\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[82,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[82,1]},"title":"roughness"},{"children":[],"comments":"Extract the raw Number value\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[110,1]},"title":"unwrap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to Number (passthrough for this type)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"toNumber"},{"children":[],"comments":"Bounds documentation for this type\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Bounded"],"NumberBounds"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[118,1]},"title":"bounds"},{"children":[],"comments":"Mirror smooth (perfect reflections)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[90,1]},"title":"mirror"},{"children":[],"comments":"Glossy (polished metal, wet surfaces)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[94,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[94,1]},"title":"glossy"},{"children":[],"comments":"Semi-rough (plastic, wood)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[98,23],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[98,1]},"title":"semiRough"},{"children":[],"comments":"Matte (fabric, paper, diffuse)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[102,1]},"title":"matte"},{"children":[],"comments":"Blend two roughness values with weight (0.0 = all first, 1.0 = all second)\n\nLinear interpolation between two roughness values. Critical for PBR material\ntransitions and procedural weathering effects:\n```purescript\nblend 0.0 mirror matte  -- Roughness 0.0\nblend 0.5 mirror matte  -- Roughness 0.5\nblend 1.0 mirror matte  -- Roughness 1.0\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,55],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[134,1]},"title":"blend"},{"children":[],"comments":"Linear interpolation (alias for blend with reversed argument order)\n\nStandard lerp signature matching shader conventions:\n```purescript\nlerp mirror matte 0.5  -- Roughness 0.5 (halfway)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[145,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[145,1]},"title":"lerp"},{"children":[],"comments":"Scale roughness value by a factor\n\nUseful for procedural material variations:\n```purescript\nscale 0.5 matte         -- Roughness 0.5\nscale 2.0 (roughness 0.3)  -- Roughness 0.6\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[155,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[155,1]},"title":"scale"},{"children":[],"comments":"Add to roughness value (clamped)\n\nIncreases roughness (makes more matte):\n```purescript\nadd 0.2 (roughness 0.3)  -- Roughness 0.5\nadd 0.5 (roughness 0.8)  -- Roughness 1.0 (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[165,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[165,1]},"title":"add"},{"children":[],"comments":"Subtract from roughness value (clamped)\n\nDecreases roughness (makes more glossy):\n```purescript\nsubtract 0.2 (roughness 0.5)  -- Roughness 0.3\nsubtract 0.5 (roughness 0.3)  -- Roughness 0.0 (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[175,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[175,1]},"title":"subtract"},{"children":[],"comments":"Invert roughness (1.0 - value)\n\nConverts roughness to smoothness and vice versa. Some engines use smoothness\n(Unity Standard) while others use roughness (Unreal, Blender):\n```purescript\ninvert (roughness 0.3)  -- Roughness 0.7\ninvert mirror           -- Roughness 1.0 (matte)\ninvert matte            -- Roughness 0.0 (mirror)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[187,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[187,1]},"title":"invert"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert roughness to smoothness (1.0 - roughness)\n\nUnity's Standard shader uses smoothness instead of roughness:\n```purescript\ntoSmoothness mirror  -- 1.0 (perfectly smooth)\ntoSmoothness matte   -- 0.0 (not smooth at all)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[197,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[197,1]},"title":"toSmoothness"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert from smoothness to roughness (1.0 - smoothness)\n\nImport from Unity or other smoothness-based workflows:\n```purescript\nfromSmoothness 1.0  -- Roughness 0.0 (mirror)\nfromSmoothness 0.0  -- Roughness 1.0 (matte)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[207,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[207,1]},"title":"fromSmoothness"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if mirror smooth (roughness = 0.0)\n\nPerfectly smooth surfaces have perfect specular reflection with no diffusion.\nThese are rare in nature but common in idealized rendering:\n```purescript\nisMirror mirror  -- true\nisMirror glossy  -- false\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[222,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[222,1]},"title":"isMirror"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if glossy (roughness <= 0.3)\n\nGlossy surfaces have visible reflections with some blur. Includes polished\nmetal, wet surfaces, lacquered wood, etc.:\n```purescript\nisGlossy glossy           -- true (0.2)\nisGlossy mirror           -- true (0.0)\nisGlossy (roughness 0.3)  -- true\nisGlossy semiRough        -- false (0.6)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[235,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[235,1]},"title":"isGlossy"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if semi-rough (0.3 < roughness < 0.8)\n\nSemi-rough surfaces have blurred reflections. Common for plastics, most\nwood, concrete, etc.:\n```purescript\nisSemiRough semiRough        -- true (0.6)\nisSemiRough (roughness 0.5)  -- true\nisSemiRough glossy           -- false\nisSemiRough matte            -- false\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[248,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[248,1]},"title":"isSemiRough"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if matte (roughness >= 0.8)\n\nMatte surfaces have completely diffused reflections with no visible specular.\nIncludes fabric, paper, unpolished stone, etc.:\n```purescript\nisMatte matte            -- true (1.0)\nisMatte (roughness 0.8)  -- true\nisMatte semiRough        -- false (0.6)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[260,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[260,1]},"title":"isMatte"}],"name":"Hydrogen.Schema.Spatial.Roughness","reExports":[]}